-------------------------------------------DESIGN-------------------------------------------
So, I made a prototype, where I thought of solving wire entanglement problem using Bearings.

Later I figured out, it wasn't a proper solution that solution.
After some research got to know, there exist Slip Rings.

So I made custom sensor mount personalized to my project requirement.

Once, I will be satisfied with my design, I will send the design for 3D printing.

